span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"error\">error</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>details 已知错误</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">The location <span class=\"keyword\">function</span> has been stopped because you <span class=\"keyword\">do</span> not agree with the privacy compliance policy. Please recheck the setAgreePrivacy interface</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>solve 解决方案</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>such as figure 1 取消下列文件中对应行的注释即可解决</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2023/03/06/baidumapuse/solve.png\" class=\"lazyload placeholder\" data-srcset=\"/2023/03/06/baidumapuse/solve.png\" srcset=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"see-参考\">see 参考</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/czy_1995/article/details/128342280\">https://blog.csdn.net/czy_1995/article/details/128342280</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"about-me-个人微信\">about me 个人微信</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://czq-blog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/me.jpeg?Expires=1741078870&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=TMP.3Kqnu2nGq3bZ4KHKg3CKb4cix6tBsmx7Nhi7A7qcv84ZvM8W24oGTuKCih6se8FQJtPuh8fHNK6NqbkbsbkDAwGCfmeBHV&amp;Signature=3OQ42kDkDuA1517Z6lKc2ZUhiQU%3D\" class=\"lazyload placeholder\" data-srcset=\"https://czq-blog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/me.jpeg?Expires=1741078870&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=TMP.3Kqnu2nGq3bZ4KHKg3CKb4cix6tBsmx7Nhi7A7qcv84ZvM8W24oGTuKCih6se8FQJtPuh8fHNK6NqbkbsbkDAwGCfmeBHV&amp;Signature=3OQ42kDkDuA1517Z6lKc2ZUhiQU%3D\" srcset=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"wechat-offical-微信公众号\">wechat offical 微信公众号</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://czq-blog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/wechat.jpg?Expires=1741078900&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=TMP.3Kqnu2nGq3bZ4KHKg3CKb4cix6tBsmx7Nhi7A7qcv84ZvM8W24oGTuKCih6se8FQJtPuh8fHNK6NqbkbsbkDAwGCfmeBHV&amp;Signature=y3fPR2LjlkZXW%2FAQCh